      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken incredible care of it, and it's been garage-kept since day one. If you're looking for a total gem that's ready for the road, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
