    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously calibrated. To ensure longevity, both the rod bearings and the rear subframe\u2014critical points for this chassis\u2014have been professionally addressed and reinforced. The six-speed longitudinal manual gearbox provides precise gate engagement, feeding power through a variable M differential lock. The factory suspension geometry remains true, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. The exterior finish and interior trim remain in showroom condition, free of the typical wear found on high-performance analogs.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
